Cookie Rejector — Privacy Policy
Cookie Rejector does not collect, transmit, or share any personal data.
What is stored locally:
A count of declined cookie banners and a list of the last 50 domain names where a banner was declined. This data is stored on your device only using Chrome's local storage API and is never sent anywhere.
What is not collected:
No browsing history, page content, personal information, or identifiable data is collected or transmitted.
Third parties:
No data is shared with any third party. The extension makes no external network requests.
